{
  "version": 2
}
```

And rename `dsahub.html` → `index.html`.

Vercel automatically serves `index.html` as the root — it won't auto-serve a custom-named HTML file without routing config.

**So your final structure should be:**
```
your-project/
├── api/
│   └── ai.js
├── index.html        ← renamed from dsahub.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── package.json